---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Terms & Conditions — Chitti" description="Terms and conditions for using Chitti — your AI beauty companion.">

  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-light">Last updated: 28 March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-policy mt-12 space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            By downloading, installing, accessing, or using the Chitti mobile application ("the App"), you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions ("Terms"). These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you and Chitti. If you do not agree to these Terms in their entirety, you must not download, install, or use the App.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Your continued use of the App following any modifications to these Terms constitutes acceptance of those modifications. We encourage you to review these Terms periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Chitti is an AI-powered beauty companion application that provides personalised skincare, haircare, and makeup guidance. The Service comprises the following features and capabilities:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Vibe Check:</strong> Instant full-look style feedback from a single selfie photo, providing spatial feedback with per-region analysis of makeup, hair, outfit, accessories, and posture. Images are processed in real-time and are never stored.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Skin Analysis:</strong> A comprehensive three-image assessment (front, left, and right facial angles) that evaluates skin condition attributes including skin type, dark circles, acne, pores, hydration levels, skin undertone, and skin depth. Images are processed in real-time and deleted immediately after analysis.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Makeup Feedback:</strong> Photo-based makeup and style analysis from selfie images, delivering structured feedback organised into positives, areas for improvement, and quick fixes. Feedback is available in multiple persona styles and supports English and Hinglish. Images are retained securely for up to 7 days to support the analysis workflow, after which they are automatically and permanently deleted.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">General Chat:</strong> Free-form conversational AI guidance for skincare, haircare, and general beauty advice, with access to product recommendations, web search, and personalised insights based on your profile.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Product Intelligence:</strong> Analysis of beauty products via URL or image, providing structured verdicts on suitability, ingredient breakdowns, routine-fit analysis, community feedback summaries, and geo-targeted purchase links.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Product Management:</strong> Tools for adding, organising, and managing your skincare, haircare, and makeup products, including morning/evening routine building with layering sequences.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">User Memory:</strong> An intelligent system that extracts your preferences and relevant facts from conversations (e.g., skin type, allergies, product preferences) to personalise future interactions without requiring you to repeat information.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
